#' Medical Decision
#'
#' Function for Medical Decision Analysis. Sensitivity, specificity, positive 
#' predictive value, negative predictive value.
#' 
#'
#' @examples
#' \dontrun{
#' # example will be added
#'}
#' @param data The data as a data frame.
#' @param gold .
#' @param goldPositive .
#' @param newtest .
